onal%22%3Atrue%7D)(%7B%22crop%22%3A%22promo%22%2C%22promo%22%3A%22the-coronavirus-crisis%22%7D) --\>\u003cdiv class=\"promote-embed\" data-promo=\"the-coronavirus-crisis\" data-crop=\"promo\">\u003c/div>\u003c!-- END-BLOCK(promote-promo)[0] --\>\n\u003cp>Greece&#8217;s prime minister, Kyriakos Mitsotakis, has used Twitter not to attack regional officials or complain about the lockdown&#8217;s impact on the economy, but to share a video showing how successful the drive to empty the nation&#8217;s streets has been.\u003c/p>\n\u003cp>\u003c!-- BLOCK(oembed)[2](%7B%7D)(%7B%22embedHtml%22%3A%22%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22el%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%2C%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%2C%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3A%20%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F.%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F.%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F%3F.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ft.co%5C%2FFRBUYeeqXg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%5C%2FFRBUYeeqXg%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%3C%5C%2Fp%3E%26mdash%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20GR%20%28%40PrimeministerGR%29%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ftwitter.com%5C%2FPrimeministerGR%5C%2Fstatus%5C%2F1247943669442846720%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%208%2C%202020%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%3C%5C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cscript%20async%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Fplatform.twitter.com%5C%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22