61\">defensive look-how-well-we&#8217;re-doing drivel\u003c/a>.&#8221; At one news conference before he became infected with Covid-19, Prime Minister Boris Johnson even shared the Trump-like boast that he had continued to shake hands, even while visiting a hospital treating coronavirus patients.\u003c/p>\n\u003cp>\u003c!-- BLOCK(oembed)[11](%7B%7D)(%7B%22embedHtml%22%3A%22%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20at%20a%20hospital%20the%20other%20night%20where%20I%20think%20there%20were%20actually%20a%20few%20coronavirus%20patients%20and%20I%20shook%20hands%20with%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBoris%20Johnson%20says%20he%20has%20not%20refused%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20people%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ftwitter.com%5C%2Fhashtag%5C%2FCOVID19%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26amp%3Bref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23COVID19%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%20outbreak.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMore%20on%20this%20story%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ft.co%5C%2F6N1ZLNKpvT%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ft.co%5C%2F6N1ZLNKpvT%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ft.co%5C%2FyV1qkQkDkh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%5C%2FyV1qkQkDkh%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%3C%5C%2Fp%3E%26mdash%3B%20SkyNews%20%28%40SkyNews%29%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ftwitter.com%5C%2FSkyNews%5C%2Fstatus%5C%2F1234842251496493060%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%203%2C%202020%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%3C%5C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cscript%20async%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Fplatform.twitter.com%5C%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22utf-8%5C%22%3E%3C%5C%2Fscript%3E%22%2C%22endpoint%22%3A%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Fapi.twitter.com%5C%2F1%5C%2Fstatuses%5C%2Foembed.json%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22twitter%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ftwitter.com%5C%2FSkyNews%5C%2Fstatus%5C%2F1234842251496493060%22%7D) --\>\u003cbr />\n\u003cblockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\">\n\u003cp