, Dr. Fahrettin Koca, to deliver \u003ca href=\"https://www.aa.com.tr/en/latest-on-coronavirus-outbreak/turkeys-death-toll-from-coronavirus-rises-to-908/1799015\">science-based, daily updates\u003c/a> on the effort to combat its spread.\u003c/p>\n\u003cp>\u003c!-- BLOCK(oembed)[13](%7B%7D)(%7B%22embedHtml%22%3A%22%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22tr%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%3FI%20%5Cu00c7ALI%3FMALARI%20%3F%5Cu00c7%3FN%20%5Cu00f6ncelikle%20ba%3Far%3Flmas%3F%20gereken%2C%20vir%5Cu00fcs%5Cu00fcn%20izole%20edilmesiydi.%20%3Fki%20bilim%20adam%3Fm%3Fz%20bunu%20ba%3Farm%3F%3F%20durumdalar.%20Erciyes%20%5Cu00dcniversitesi%5Cu2019nden%20Prof.%20Dr.%20AYKUT%20%5Cu00d6ZDARENDEL%3F%20Hocam%3Fz%3F%2C%20Ankara%20%5Cu00dcniversitesi%5Cu2019nden%20Prof.%20Dr.%20AYKUT%20%5Cu00d6ZKUL%20Hocam%3Fz%3F%20halk%3Fm%3Fz%20ad%3Fna%20kutluyorum.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ft.co%5C%2FPGYCsVosxw%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%5C%2FPGYCsVosxw%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%3C%5C%2Fp%3E%26mdash%3B%20Dr.%20Fahrettin%20Koca%20%28%40drfahrettinkoca%29%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ftwitter.com%5C%2Fdrfahrettinkoca%5C%2Fstatus%5C%2F1247796413192265729%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%208%2C%202020%3C%5C%2Fa%3E%3C%5C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cscript%20async%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Fplatform.twitter.com%5C%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22utf-8%5C%22%3E%3C%5C%2Fscript%3E%22%2C%22endpoint%22%3A%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Fapi.twitter.com%5C%2F1%5C%2Fstatuses%5C%2Foembed.json%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22twitter%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%5C%2F%5C%2Ftwitter.com%5C%2Fdrfahrettinkoca%5C%2Fstatus%5C%2F1247796413192265729%22%7D) --\>\u003cbr />\n\u003cblockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\">\n\u003cp lang=\"tr\" dir=\"ltr\">A?I ÇALI?MALARI ?Ç?N öncelikle ba?ar?lmas? gereken, virüsün izole edilmesiydi. ?ki bilim adam?m?z bunu ba?arm?? durumdalar. Erciyes Üniversitesi’nden Prof. Dr. AYKUT ÖZDARENDEL? Hocam?z?, Ankara Ün